us，頭兩年有3個rotation，兩年後大概40幾k+bonus。rotation應該都係corp bank嘅唔同team或者function rotate，完左兩年program之後跟咩team要睇自己造化。雖然人工高，但前景睇落麻麻，首先行頭窄，點跳都係bank；其次小弟怕中資有入無出，唔知係咪真。<br />\n<br />\n小弟係普通3大bba major會計，唔識technical電腦嘢，想知道做cyber security會唔會好多嘢學handle唔到。如果我覺得未來前途/錢途 &gt;&gt;&gt; fresh grad收入/個人興趣，應該點樣揀？跪求各位ching比多d意見我，特別係cyber security前景/工作內容方面，感謝<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T07:05:22.000Z","msg":"聽講只要熟讀內容就唔難考。見senior manager話呢條team好處係發展階段升職快<br />\n<br />\nEY啲on9口號黎<br />\n所謂啲乜春發展階段team如cyber sec CCaSS<br />\n有邊條team唔係柒唔係奶屎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3758caab9cae5b87dd834ce79a53d6a18b8b522f","tid":1277001,"uid":266172,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ef91e5e8418b30e7ea08869cde366e8edfe11596","tid":1277001,"uid":57549,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"a7db1f83dc0f97f09b2a75f7855dd6505cb2a230","tid":1277001,"uid":3312,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3d2c2959dff407418c6f75c8dd3fe72bc16fe35b","tid":1277001,"uid":168716,"like":4,"dislike":5,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T06:00:14.000Z","msg":"唔好入建行<br />\n我明佢current packages 好靚<br />\n但你要諗真d以後條路點部署"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T06:31:40.000Z","msg":"同意ching話要諗真d，我都驚揀錯，賺頭蝕尾，所以都係想了解多d做it cyber security條路會係點"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T06:35:43.000Z","msg":"cyber security 冇得做<br />\n香港人唔重視"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T07:08:55.000Z","msg":"cyber security前途無限，但你要係hacker，唔係做compliance."},{"pid":"9cf060b61a0d3d7adbd24db7d0268a6356832cc9","tid":1277001,"uid":57549,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3758caab9cae5b87dd834ce79a53d6a18b8b522f","tid":1277001,"uid":266172,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ef91e5e8418b30e7ea08869cde366e